@startuml MSG3_Maximo_UseCases
!theme plain
skinparam actorStyle awesome

title MSG-3 → Maximo Integration - Use Cases

left to right direction

actor "Engineering\nTeam" as engineer
actor "Maintenance\nPlanner" as planner
actor "System Admin" as admin
actor "Maximo\nSystem" as maximo

rectangle "MSG-3 Maximo Integration" {
  
  usecase (Upload MSG-3 Excel) as UC1
  usecase (Validate MSG-3 Data) as UC2
  usecase (Detect Changes) as UC3
  usecase (Map to Maximo) as UC4
  usecase (Send to Maximo) as UC5
  usecase (View Integration Report) as UC6
  usecase (Configure Mapping Rules) as UC7
  usecase (View Integration History) as UC8
  usecase (Handle Errors) as UC9
  usecase (Redesign MSG-3 Template) as UC10
  
  UC1 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
  UC2 ..> UC3 : <<include>>
  UC3 ..> UC4 : <<include>>
  UC4 ..> UC5 : <<include>>
  UC5 ..> UC6 : <<include>>
  
  UC2 ..> UC9 : <<extend>>
  UC5 ..> UC9 : <<extend>>
}

engineer --> UC1
engineer --> UC6
engineer --> UC10
planner --> UC6
admin --> UC7
admin --> UC8
UC5 --> maximo

note right of UC1
  FE1: Gebruiker kan MSG-3 Excel uploaden
  - Original formaat
  - Redesign formaat
  - Valideer bestandsformaat
end note

note right of UC2
  FE2: Validatie van structuur en inhoud
  - Verplichte velden
  - Datatypes
  - Business rules
  - ATA codes
end note

note right of UC3
  FE3: Wijzigingsregistratie
  - Vergelijk met vorige versie
  - Detecteer: added, modified, deleted
  - Genereer changelog
end note

note right of UC4
  FE4: Mapping naar Maximo objecten
  - MSG-3 Task → PM
  - MSG-3 Task → JobPlan
  - Configureerbare mappingregels
end note

note right of UC5
  FE5: Versturen naar Maximo
  - REST API calls
  - Create/Update PM's
  - Create/Update JobPlans
  - Error handling & retry
end note

note right of UC6
  FE6: Rapportage
  - Aantal verwerkte taken
  - Aantal fouten
  - Changelog overzicht
  - Logging details
end note

@enduml
